question:
\begin{array}{l}
\text { B-5. Evaluate }\\
\sum_{k=0}^{n}(-1)^{k}\binom{n}{k}(x-k)^{n} .
\end{array}

solution:
\begin{array}{l}
\text { B-5. }\\
\text { The sum is } n!\text { since it is an } n \text {th difference of a monic polynomial, } x^{n} \text {, of degree } n \text {. }
\end{array}

